name: Operations Control Room
description:
Dear Hic Et Nunc artists, fans, collectors, and beyond....

It’s Enoch Root here sending you this NFT from the year 5075. Actually NFTs haven’t existed in years. They were converted to Galact=k SunRa tokens with a special Interstellar Space I.S. Wallet in the year 3026. I won’t bore you with the details. You folks back on earth just started minting NFTs, and as I understand the party is just getting started. One piece of unsolicited advice from 5075: Keep minting your digital assets and supporting each other. You will be rewarded beyond your imagination. 
This is the operations control room here on cargo ship Meadowsweet. I know, “it’s a digital version.” The Federation doesn’t allow cameras these days. And that’s ok I guess. It’s not like we are into cattle rustling and train heists! Hmmmm… wait we actually do like those. They’re good for business. 

Keep on flyin’....Love, Enoch
